{"tid":214783,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實一人一票有咩咁好？有冇人係唔支持一人一票？","createTime":"2017-04-24T03:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T18:26:39.000Z","uid":90,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da45e6595256508b60bd5ac24fdad72ebcf1d91c","tid":214783,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啫係唔係話睇唔起人<br />\n但有啲人真係唔需要有票<br />\n個人好似唔識分析,甚至支持啲咩都唔知<br />\n（e.g部份黃絲，最具體就雷動投自決個班）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人覺得選民應該係要被篩選<br />\n唔一定係話學歷，家底上去分辨<br />\n但係以一種合理嘅形式去篩選有腦嘅人去投"},{"pid":"613dd068f0b841532d8955f05a8ed65e7203f0a6","tid":214783,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"一人一票未必係好 <br />\n但你d理據睇的出你無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24a7e8dc96ccaca4ccf1414dd0c22cf723d423b","tid":214783,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"唔係太識講（因為我都唔係好明）<br />\n但係有冇人知我指啲咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啫係有啲人可能覺得大學生好醒好勁<br />\n廢老小學畢業好廢好垃圾<br />\n但係有啲位，部份廢老仲心水清<br />\n啲大學生都冇咁清<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識點講..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係我立場過激<br />\n睇唔起其他立場嘅人<br />\n覺得人地蠢，揀錯？"},{"pid":"db9e98f571784a8eff828332137bc29bc500beca","tid":214783,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一人一票未必係好 <br />\n但你d理據睇的出你無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我腦入面都未諗好點講<br />\n是但將啲零散嘅idea打上嚟<br />\n想拋磚引玉去完整下我個idea咋<br />\n<br />\n我都知我啲理據唔好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為鳩打出嚟"},{"pid":"ea7407ff89cc528e7aee36b96c6422f1a7079d8d","tid":214783,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:33:08.000Z","msg":"民主選舉既目的唔係為你心目中人選得到勝利既工具"},{"pid":"8ff760bbdb45c785a0de5cd491e87d00d7aaf008","tid":214783,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一人一票未必係好 <br />\n但你d理據睇的出你無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我腦入面都未諗好點講<br />\n是但將啲零散嘅idea打上嚟<br />\n想拋磚引玉去完整下我個idea咋<br />\n<br />\n我都知我啲理據唔好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為鳩打出嚟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢點我認我咁講無腦<br />\n因為呢個諗法，我自已都未完全明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係完全明嘅嘢係講到1999咁"},{"pid":"9d3bd95fb4393ce3a030b920babf25102db75ed4","tid":214783,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主選舉既目的唔係為你心目中人選得到勝利既工具</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱<br />\n但好似好多人都當咗係..."},{"pid":"e8538a66f9e99f1328bd51ce743f1d028c7dedd5","tid":214783,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"因為要平衡所有持份者"},{"pid":"bbe1e2a83e679aeb6d6a26c0b2cad03676df408e","tid":214783,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主選舉既目的唔係為你心目中人選得到勝利既工具</blockquote><br />\n收返依句，因為理解錯既話就變左另一個意思<br />\n民主選舉主要目的係防止最惡劣既情況發生時，難以推翻，因為推翻既本成太高，例如戰爭"},{"pid":"d18f01886a7204d6416bfcba17e09ea696971944","tid":214783,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>民主選舉既目的唔係為你心目中人選得到勝利既工具</blockquote><br />\n收返依句，因為理解錯既話就變左